text: Improved Orion rocket shortly after launch. Improved Orion is the designation of an American sounding rocket. It has a maximum flight altitude of 85 km, a liftoff thrust of 7.00 kN, a total mass of 400 kg, a core diameter of 0.35 m and a total length of 5.60 m. ==See also== * Terrier Orion ==External links== * Detailed information Category:Sounding rockets of the United States
title: Improved Orion
